Eva Kor embraced Oskar Groening in court last week for his alleged role in the murder of 300,000 Jews at Auschwitz . 
  She called for the prosecutions of former SS officers to end . 
  Her co-plaintiffs said she should not have taken part in the trial in Germany . 
  Mrs Kor said she could not forgive Groening for his role in murders . 
